high_descs: Turn right and walk to the door then turn right and walk to the small black table.
Pick up the spoon that's furthest away from you on the black table.
Put the spoon in the mug that's above the salt on the black table.
Pick up the mug with the spoon in it.
Turn around and take a step to your left and walk to the black table in front of you.
Put the mug on the table near you.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the small black table in the left corner.
Pick up the spoon on the table.
Put the spoon in the mug on the table.
Pick up the mug with spoon on the table.
Turn around, bring the mug with spoon to the round black table.
Put the mug with spoon on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with spoon on the black round table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the small black table near the door
Pick up the spoon from the table
Put the spoon in the mug
Pick up the mug and spoon from the table
Turn around and go to the black round table in the corner
Place the mug and spoon on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon and a mug on a table
